headline: Cadence Announces Third Quarter 2025 Financial Results Webcast
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., October 03, 2025--Cadence (Nasdaq: CDNS) will hold its third quarter 2025 financial results webcast on Monday, October 27, 2025

headline: Cadence (CDNS) Upgraded to Buy: Here's What You Should Know
summary: Cadence (CDNS) has been upgraded to a Zacks Rank #2 (Buy), reflecting growing optimism about the company's earnings prospects. This might drive the stock higher in the near term.
